quran[8{c,v,t}:
17,97,"jis ko Allah hadaayat day wohi hadaayat panay wala hai, aur jisay woh gumraahi mein daal day to uskay siwa aisay logon ke liye to koi haami o nasir nahi pa sakta un logon ko hum qayamat ke roz avndhe mun khech layein ge, andhay, gungay aur behray unn ka thikana jahannum hai jab kabhi is ki aag dheemi honay lagey gi hum usay aur bahrakna den ge"
17,98,"yeh badla hai un ki is harkat ka ke unhon ne hamari ayaat ka inkaar kya aur kaha"" kya jab hum sirf haddiyan aur khaak ho kar reh jayen ge to naye suray se hum ko peda kar ke utha khara kya jaye ga? """
17,99,"kya un ko yeh nah soojha ke jis khuda ne zameen aurAasmanon ko peda kya hai woh inn jeson ko peda karne ki zaroor qudrat rakhta hai? is ne inn ke hashar ke liye aik waqt muqarrar kar rakha hai jis ka aana yakeeni hai, magar zaalmon ko israar hai ke woh is ka inkaar hi karen ge"
17,100,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn se kaho, agar kahin mere rab ki rehmat ke khazanay tumahray qabzay mein hotay to tum kharch ho jaane ke andaishay se zaroor un ko rok rakhtay waqai ensaan bara tang dil waqay howa hai"
17,101,"hum ne moose ko to nishanain ataa ki theen jo Sarih tor par dikhayi day rahi theen ab yeh tum khud bani Israel se pooch lau ke jab woh samnay ayen to firaon ne yahi kaha tha na ke"" ae moose, mein samjhta hon ke to zaroor aik sehar zada aadmi hai """
17,102,"moose ne is ke jawab mein kaha"" to khoob jaanta hai ke yeh baseerat Afroz nishanain Rab-us- Samwat -o -walarz ke siwa kisi ne nazil nahi ki hain, aur mera khayaal yeh hai ke ae firaon, to zaroor aik shamat zada aadmi hai """
17,103,"aakhir kaar firaon ne iradah kya ke moose aur bani Israel ko zameen se ukhaar phainky, magar hum ne is ko aur iss ke sathiyon ko akhatta ghark kar diya"
17,104,"aur is ke baad bani Israel se kaha ke ab tum zameen mein bso, phir jab akhirat ke waday ka waqt aan poora hoga to hum tum sab ko aik sath laa haazir karen ge"
